description: Earth Invasion: 13 July 2012 Will we survive the Earth Invasion? Mankind is in dire straits as a ruthless mafia operation from an advanced alien civilization is the attacking the Earth. Find out how an alien defector can help the Earth survive the ravages of his former bosses in a desperate fight for survival! First issue of an ongoing series.
name: 13 July 2012

description: Earth Invasion: Fight or Flight? The mafia from outer space is here and are terrorizing the Earth! The alien mafia sends an elite Assassination team to recapture their unwilling crew member. Our heroes must keep the alien defector Grzzt alive no matter what! With the help of the alien defector Grzzt's technological skills, can humans and animals team up in order for the Earth to survive?
name: Fight or Flight?

description: Earth Invasion: New Recruits The experimental Human - Animal Combat Team is completed. The military has ordered their first mission. Their target is to terminate a cell of rich and influential human traitors who are working with the alien mafia. Can humans and animals continue to work together to fight the alien mafia and human traitors?
name: New Recruits

description: Earth Invasion: Now What? Though the team's first mission was successful, things just got more complex for its' members. The humans are ordered to house the animals in their homes; which is quite challenging, as they are a bear and a tiger! As Nina and Darryl, both of whom live with their families, return to their respective homes with their unexpected boarders, they recall their pasts. Both homes will never be the same once the large predators take up residence!
name: Now What?

description: Earth Invasion: Reprisal The adjustment period of the large predators living with the families of their human partners continues uneasily. Meanwhile, Grzzt explains more about his kind and why they are doing what they are doing.
name: Reprisal

description: Earth Invasion: Honeymoon As humanity is still reeling from the Kazoop's attack on Fort Knox, Grzzt is taken to a secret meeting with the General Secretary. Unbeknownst to them, the meeting is not so secret. Meanwhile, we learn more about Kevin Keene and Martha Cortez.
name: Honeymoon

description: The Marvel Chess Collection is a bi-weekly series offering the comic fan and chess lover alike the chance to collect a unique chess set, featuring some of the greatest and most loved Marvel characters. The second set in the Marvel Chess Collection features the X-Men versus their greatest foes. How will Cyclops cope against the metal-master Magneto? Will high-flying Archangel be struck down by Sabertooth? Can Storm deal with Deathbird? With the Marvel Chess Collection the mighty mutant battle is in your hands.
name: Mystique [Black Bishop]

description: The Marvel Chess Collection is a bi-weekly series offering the comic fan and chess lover alike the chance to collect a unique chess set, featuring some of the greatest and most loved Marvel characters. The second set in the Marvel Chess Collection features the X-Men versus their greatest foes. How will Cyclops cope against the metal-master Magneto? Will high-flying Archangel be struck down by Sabertooth? Can Storm deal with Deathbird? With the Marvel Chess Collection the mighty mutant battle is in your hands.

description: Time is Not on Our Side If you are not good enough for Heaven, or bad enough for Hell, where do you go? The new team at the Time Corps Venice Beach sub-station barely has any time to settle in when they get their next assignment -- to chase down a wayward Spartan hoplite in full battle array.

Thermoplyae

As the chase for the wayward Spartan hoplite gets more serious, intrigue moves along in both the future and the Celestial Bureaucracy home office.

Kirklau teaches his impressionable teenage son Kostya how to shoot a rifle and is interrupted by news of defecting German soldiers. Kirklau informs his Lieutenant General (and brother in law) Wolfgang that there is a mole and orders Wolfgang to find him and deal with him.

Treadwater goes into Germany to steal the missile from Kirklau. The team has to infiltrate a highly secure military base, but despite overwhelming odds, they are successful. But when they bring the warhead back to their base to dismantle it, they find a surprise inside... a stowaway.

Wolfgang strikes a deal with Treadwater. If they can retrieve his nephew (unharmed) from Germany, he will provide them the location of the second warhead. Unsure if they can trust Wolfgang, the team has no choice but to accede to Wolfgang's request before Kirklau has time to arm the second warhead.

Chapter Titles

  • Chapter 64: Ittekimasu
  • Extra: Welcome Back
  • Chapter 65: Pink Spider - Part I
  • Chapter 66: Pink Spider - Part II

description:
Which Way is Up

A loving family descends into bickering and hatred when they can't agree which road to take.
name: Which Way Is Up

description: The mayhem has hit the news, and snappy reporter Lydia Perez smells a story. Meanwhile, Agent Paulson has plenty to explain to his wife...

Alaric Moebius and Basil Fox follow the trail of the lost Nazi Foo Fighter prototype all the way to Tokyo, where an annoying run in with ninjas bring them one step closer to their quarry… and another step into their competition's clutches! Its all they can do to dodge Mercenaries, South American pirates, and... a beautiful shape-changing squid-monster? Part 2 in the 4-part adventure "The Shadow Gambit!"
name: The Shadow Gambit! Part 3

description:
Akacya’s still looking for that evil Medic and she needs to go against “Messy” the psycho Hunter. All this will bring them in the middle of the ocean. Deep deep under!.

X21E4 (A.K.A North America) 2155. The population is divided in 3 major groups. The high class, the low class and the Infected. When someone needs someone arrested or killed. It’s easier to call for a Bounty Hunter. They are hundreds in X21E4 but the one on top of the list is AKACYA

The Silver Age

An impossible army of mad alien gods approach the Earth. With his back against the wall. our Super Wizard peers across the gulf of history to find versions of himself from a simpler time.

Can he trust a massively overpowered Silver Age Super Wizard because if he's a tremendous dick? Or the Atomic American Super Wizard? And what dark desires hide behind the Underground Super Wizard...?

Can our hero build an army to protect us? Or are we doomed?
name: The Silver Age

description: TV reporter Bridget Primavera gets her own reality show, following her exploits as she takes on the spirit of the superpowered Celtic goddess Brighid in modern-day Atlanta, kicking butt and taking names. Everything seems to be going her way, but there's something not quite right. It turns out the hardest battles aren't actually fought against the "bad guys" after all.

volume.name: The Ballad of Brighid of Atlanta

description:
From the creators of Afterlife Inc. and 7STRING comes Big Punch Magazine, a quarterly magazine serialising four brand new series from the Big Punch Multiverse.

The action continues in BPM issue 2! The crew of the Reflektor find more than they bargained for when a simple transaction takes them into uncharted multiversal territories... and deep and dangerous waters; New York trembles as the mysterious Orb manifests in turbulent skies, bringing down the wrath of the Paragons; armed with a talking (and disgruntled) sword, Elsie Blackwood comes face to face with the force of nature that is Tyler Goldensheath; and in the walled city of Prizm, Cyanne and her team must contend with the Elite Catchers in a battle to defend their home!

The World's Greatest Barbarian Detective continues his adventures in a weird world of hard boiled fantasy. Some comic book heroes live forever. Others die all the time. Collecting the next three stories in the "Dozen Deaths" story arc.
name: Book Two: A Dozen Deaths

description: Two men, in the face of a ravaged, haunted land, burdened with responsibilities they could never foresee and an enemy they could never imagine, must choose what type of people they wish to be in the broken days to come.

Cold Starts

In modern-day Sunflower Hills, Kenneth has shed the Conjuror. He finds new purpose after wasted millennia of desperate attempts to rescue Rhianna from the City of Dis. His old adversary, Abbadon, however, finds a new way to goad Kenneth into trying, again, for a Portal back to that infernal world.
name: Cold Starts

description:
The Great War, July 1917. At an isolated stretch of the Front, French and German soldiers kill each other in an endless carnage...

The night air is rent by sentries' screams. Everyone in the French camp thinks it's a trap laid by the enemy, but soon they hear screams from the German lines... With both factions being hunted, they are obliged to declare a uneasy truce and send a team of men to solve the mystery. With them goes Wohati, a Cree Warrior, one of the 12,000 Indians in the U.S. Army, and the only man who knows what's waiting out there...

The Assassination Conspiracy

A mutated cybernetic boar searches for his place in the world. Looking for peace, Cy-boar usually finds only danger, and skull splitting action!

CY-BOAR #9: THE ASSASSINATION CONSPIRACY

What would you do if you awoke to find you'd just assassinated a senator in the capitol building? Cy-Boar finds out in this tale of mind control, corruption and cybernetic super soldiers!
name: The Assassination Conspiracy

description: Reunited and it feels so... bad? Shane finds Annie, but she's, uh, full of surprises. Meanwhile, General Custer has other plans for Shane and Jack.
name: Part Three

description:
Who is the Dogcatcher?

Dober-man faces a new arch nemesis when his enemies join forces to defeat him and his canine companion! Outnumbered, Dober-man must rely on his own friends and allies to face the unified forces of villainy.

As an extra bonus, Dober-man's four page origin story is also included!
name: Who is the Dogcatcher?; Timesheet

first_appearance_teams.name: The Continental Coalition of Canine Crusaders

team_credits.name: The Continental Coalition of Canine Crusaders

description:
Game ON!

This month's comic continues the storyline launched last month as Miss Match, Elastic Man, Amazing Amazon and Mr. Fabulous are captured and transported to an organizer of exotic big-game hunting expeditions - and they're the prey! Can they quit arguing amongst themselves long enough to stay alive?

And for the Bonus Feature - oh, man! As a way to celebrate the digital release of the 416-page book, The Complete Greystone Inn, I'm grabbing all of the Greystone Inn strips from a very exciting Autumn that saw the premier of Sam Snood, a film-noir-style turkey detective as well as the Curse of Rafinesque. Plus, a quaint country Christmas (inspired by the Bad Axe, Michigan, holidays of my youth) culminates in a marriage proposal!
name: Game ON!

description: Godkiller has its own special breed of zombie, a weirder and more shocking variety than Romero or Ennis ever imagined... and our surviving heroes are surrounded by them in this epic climax to Godkiller's Walk Among Us arc.

A Phase We're Going Through Part 1

Tempest has been defeated, but a new challenge now awaits the Guardians! Who is he? What does he want? Find out here!
name: A Phase We're Going Through Part 1

description: The Viking warrioress, Aydis, reaches the inferno trapping a legendary Valkyrie leader while Aydis's horse, Saga, is left behind with mystical predators lurking.

We follow the monster to his den, only to find he's been living the suburban life. Meanwhile, Jess joins forces with a hunting team on a quest to destroy the monster. This final chapter will have you questioning the nature of good and evil to the very last page.

Funny Pages

Go back to the origins of The Inquiring Minds in this fun and exciting comic strip collection that introduces the characters and their early days.

This not a full story, but a collection of Sunday and Daily type comic strips in full color. The events here take place before the exciting first issue of the Inquiring Minds; The Ghost Pirate Skeletons of Three Craters Lake.
name: Funny Pages

description: After discovering that the women of their small town are turning into murderous monsters, Ace and Gwen escape the most recent massacre and try to figure out just what the hell is going on. Are they lesbians? Are they zombies? Either way: In this town, when Hot Girls make out, IT'S EVIL!

Bloodlines part 2 of 3

A forbidden inter-racial love affair leads to a duel; choices are made in the obscuring fog of love and honor, duty and responsibility. Defending his love of Annabelle, Hiro Sato is shot down dead by Judah Baker, her father. While Hiro's own father, Hiroshi wrestles with his conflicting loyalties, Judah, finding himself at the head of a mob, must decide what steps to take in regards to, Annabelle, his only child... and her newborn son.
name: Bloodlines Part 2 of 3

description:
Acquiesce 4 of 4

When government agencies come to archaeologist Laila McCarthy for assistance, they are unaware her knowledge of dangerous relics was gained first-hand. But ancient enemies remember her as Sumerian demon Lamashtu and the first vampire.

The big finale of the first story arc.
name: Acquiesce 4 of 4

description: Hanzo Hasashi faces his inner demon—literally—in a mirror-match to save his own soul!
name: Blood Island Chapter 32: Mirror Match

description:
Collects Myths of India: Hanuman, Myths of India: Andhaka, Myths of India: Krishna, Myths of India: Lakshmi, and Myths of India: Saraswati:

Lakshmi the daughter of sea and sister to the moon, Hanuman born with the body of an ape, but a heart as large as a hundred suns. Saraswati the white swan, Andhaka the blind one, Krishna the embodiment of divine joy. These are five powerful stories in this third compilation of the series, MYTHS OF INDIA, presented by Graphic India and Deepak Chopra. These magical retellings of immortal gods and goddesses have travelled many generations and belong to the core of Indian mythology. Each tale features a foreword by acclaimed author Deepak Chopra followed by stunning illustrations and artwork.
name: Volume 3

description: 40+ pages about desire spread over 4 stories from the best new talent in comics.
name: Volume Five: Desire

description:
Based in the Pentagon is a nameless clandestine special ops squad composed of members with special abilities. This squad is tasked with dangerous internal investigations and off the records wet-work.

THE PENTAGON #2

The Pentagon squad must protect an important Senator from the heavily armed Crimson Militia.

September 21st, 2019 - 13:13 pm

After a successful take-off, the Atlantis Shuttle disappears mysteriously from control screens.

September 22nd, 2019 - 13:13 pm

All the timepieces (watches, clocks...) on the planet suddenly stop.

September 23rd, 2019 - 13:13 pm

The Atlantis Shuttle reappears and lands in Cape Canaveral, with only one survivor is on board: the commanding officer of the mission is found in a state of shock right in the middle of his crew's torn appart corpses.

September 24th, 2019 - 13:13 pm

An American nuclear submarine gets the echo sonar of a German U-boat that had disappeared sixty eight years earlier... In open sea, a trawler discovers the monumental hull of the Titanic, that sank in the same place, 650 km in the Southeast of Newfoundland.

And that's just a beginning... As the threat of Apocalypse hangs over the whole planet, it would seem that the future of Humanity has plunged into obscurity... presaging the worst for our civilisation.
name: Atlantis 2/2

description:
Misdirection

The Odysseys are going on holiday to meet up with Doc's old army buddy, Salt. But when Salt's ship gets attacked and taken over by pirates, the Odysseys board looking for friends but find a fiendish crew instead. Can the Odysseys find out the truth before the pirates get the better of them? Come join our favorite family's maritime adventure in Misdirection.
name: Misdirection

description:
Sevara was burned alive, and Alathea - stoned to death, supposedly. But Alathea somehow survived, and has been on the run ever since. All she has is her knife, her wits, and a tiny baby she rescued along the way. But when the baby begins to grow at an alarming rate, things are not what they seem. Alathea must unlock the secret that runs through her veins before Mitan's war machine crushes them all.

In a future so distant it looks like a past, a shapeshifting immortal awakens from a ten thousand year sleep to find that the memories of her mortal life have corrupted the future.

Lawrence and Legio attack Ted Connors, the young dealer you gave methamphetamine to his son, leaving Ted mentally unhinged. Utilizing information extracted from Ted, the duo work their way up the food chain, targeting the regional suppliers and a mid-level urban crime ring. Leaving broken bodies and minds in their wake, Lawrence and Legio finally fix their sights on their primary target, a drug kingpin named, William J. Nichols.

How to stalk a Black Swan

In this 3rd issue, The Solitonus Agency is preparing to go public, when devastating news reaches them from America.

Also, the Agency's first high-profile launch, attracts some unwanted attention. Also, the security team branches out on a side project...
name: How To Stalk A Black Swan

description:
Chapter 11

While Ally is on a job, Brad and Danny go out drinking. Seth uses this to cause trouble.
name: Chapter 11

description:
A 2000 year-old secret could shatter the power of the Vatican if it came to be revealed. And some are ready to kill to know it...

To settle an old debt of honor, a Godfather in the Mafia puts his best killer at the disposal of Vatican. Angelo, a whiz kid with a gun, is hired by a powerful Cardinal, who's overseeing the execution of the Church's most discreet black-ops specialists and spies.

He will be the guardian angel of a young and beautiful investigator. Their mission will lead them to Jerusalem, in the Holy Land, and an ancient mystery.
name: Operation Judas 2/2

description:
When a portal to the underworld opens in the middle of Las Vegas, Venom must join Red Hulk, Ghost Rider and X-23 on a crusade to stop the spread of Hell on Earth. Can these tarnished heroes wrestle free of their own personal demons and band together to save the world in its darkest hour? Then, Venom faces a gauntlet of doom as Crime-Master unites Jack O’Lantern, the Human Fly, Toxin and more to destroy him! Crime-Master’s diabolical plan brings war to Flash Thompson’s family and friends — and in this war, there will be victims! Meanwhile, Venom joins the Secret Avengers, but what’s left of Flash to join the team? Even with the symbiote under control, Flash’s dark secrets put everything at risk — especially when the original Venom host, Eddie Brock, comes calling!

Collects Venom (2011) #13, 13.1-13.4, 14-22.
name: Volume 2

volume.name: Venom By Rick Remender: The Complete Collection

description:
Home Invasion

During a mission to Australia, Ambassador Benton Hawkes helped avert a war -- enraging the powers that be and making an enemy of U.S. Senator Mick Carri. On Mars, where a corporation runs the planet with a blood-red fist, a mass murder has potentially dangerous implications for Earth. Now Benton Hawkes finds himself caught between what he wants and what two planets need.
name: Home Invasion

description:
In 1915, Allied forces attempted to end the stalemate on the Western Front by advancing into the Ottoman Empire. The campaign was a failure.

Using contemporary documents such as letters home, poetry, propaganda and military records, this graphic novel explores the story of the catastrophic Gallipoli campaign, and the involvement of Inverclyde's own 5th Argylls.

The project was supported by Heritage Lottery Fund through the First World War Then And Now programme.

Suggested for mature audiences, due to scenes of warfare which some people may find upsetting or disturbing.

Princess Sophie's life is turned upside down when her brother invites his old friend to Morgan Isle. Feelings Sophie had buried away so long ago begin to resurface. The last time she saw this man was ten years ago-when she ended their secret relationship. Alex's return sends Sophie into a whirlwind of passion, but when his ulterior motives are revealed, Sophie's shattered heart turns to dust.
name: Vol. 1

description:
This edition of the ARCHIE 1000 PAGE COMICS series is JAM-PACKED with the best, funniest and most hilarious stories from Archie & his pals 'n' gals! We've got 1000 more pages of chaos and comedy for our doting fans! For over seven decades, Archie and his friends have been making everyone laugh, with their dating hijinx and misadventures at Riverdale High School! Everything's Archie in the largest Archie collection series EVER--offered at an incredible value price!

Note: The digital edition (8/5/2015) for this volume was released before the print edition.
name: TPB

description: YEE-HAW! It's time to wrangle up Archie and his pals for this new digital exclusive collection! This time, the gang is moseying around in the Ol' West, roping cattle and having milkshakes down at the saloon. Can the gang protect the town from the rowdy outlaws that wanna run this town?

NOTE: This version has language appropriate for younger readers.

A boring assignment brings local TV reporter Bridget Primavera face to face with the Cailleach -- the primeval Celtic spirit of the killing frost -- and Bridget's world changes forever. In an instant, she is awakened to her own role and responsibility as the equally ancient, balancing spirit of Brighid, teacher of poets and physicians, guardian of the hearth, and warrior of the Tuatha De Danann... as if she needed one more thing to do.

volume.name: The Ballad of Brighid of Atlanta

description: After being suddenly dispatched for a last-minute interpreting job, Alex is left speechless at the arrogant attitude of her employer, Max. Even though she is confident in her ability to do her job, Max is looking not only for a skilled interpreter, but a beautiful companion to accompany him in high-society events. After being evaluated by Max, she is forced to transform herself into a gorgeous socialite! Alex reluctantly decides to follow his demands. In the midst of things, he bluntly issues her a warning: "Don't go against me. Especially when I'm in a good mood." How far will his arrogance go?
name: Vol. 1

description:
Death Rattle

On a Tuesday afternoon a cloaked creature of chaos arrives in a small town to unleash a plague of dead babies with chainsaws in a twisted experiment of extermination!

Will the town survive!? Will they be able to vanquish the...Dead Babies with Chainsaws!!!
name: Death Rattle

description:
Battle for Nuevo Laredo

Nuevo Laredo, Mexico is a bustling city and beacon of cultural and commercial crossroads on the Texas-Mexican border; a place where El Catrin and his organization vie for control to command the important intersection. The approaching arrival of military grade weapons to the area will ensure El Catrin's dominance in the region. An informant leak leads Nuevo Laredo's Municipal Police officer, Miguel Ramos to warn El Peso Hero about the upcoming shipment in the hopes that he can put a stop to El Catrin's solidification of power in Nuevo Laredo. It is up to the paladin of justice, the protector of the border, El Peso Hero to stop the valuable shipment and confront El Catrin amidst social unrest in Nuevo Laredo.

volume.name: El Peso Hero: Battle for Nuevo Laredo

description:
La Junta: Lights Out

The grid goes down, panic sets in, and Hank finds himself alone and out of options in La Junta, Colorado. With traps in place, Hank settles in for the long haul as an intruder eyes his gun collection. Blood will be shed. This is only the beginning of the End of US.
name: La Junta: Lights Out

description:
Cold Notice

The Genocide Men keep the world safe from rebellions, pandemics, and genetic deviants. But Jacob Doe doesn't enjoy his work as a state-sanctioned mass-murderer...and he may have discovered an insurgency that he cannot kill.
name: Chapter 1 - Cold Notice

description:
Birthday

The last day of Gregory Suicide.
name: Birthday

description:
Shoo' Fly Die!!!

The Hallotweens encounter a most despicable bank robber. What good will their supernatural abilities do against their most disgusting adversary yet?
name: Shoo' Fly Die!!!

description:
Halloween Man: On a Pale Horse

From the Futuristic Streets of Solar City to Beyond the Pale! When one of Lucy's way out experiments sends Solomon to the fantastical realm of Purgatory, he finds himself facing down the legendary Four Horsemen of the Apocalypse. The battle will be a hard one, but the journey home might be harder. With crisp art by Kaan Erdogan, it is a must read for any fan of horror, sci/fi, and weird fiction.

volume.name: Halloween Man: On a Pale Horse Special

description: Can anyone stop the Northside Monster's ruthless rampage? A city lives in fear as a brutal killer runs loose on the streets. But hope arrives with a former FBI standout who cannot feel physical pain. His rare condition a power... and a curse. Will he stop the city's bleeding? Find out if our hero is up for the challenge of his life!

A special collected edition of all the Isle Squared Comics Premiere issues. Including Pale Dark, Tether, Empress, Snake and Bang Bang Lucita. Also, bonus WIP previews of Protector Vixi and Xibalba. Bonus Snake: Prologue and more!

I. Pale Dark: Issue 01 – Subject K is detained by a mysterious Pale Man, tortured and interrogated. An eerie sci-fi series featuring the art of Ruvel Abril. Pale Dark was selected as one of the Best Indie Comics Series of 2014 by ComicBastards.com.

II. Tether: Issue 01 – Alina, a young slave is thrust into the arena for the first time. Emperor Trovaar makes a decision about the future. An epic sci-fi series in the vein of Dune, Spartacus and Mad Max. Featuring the art of Alex Reis and colors of Nimesh Morarji.

III. Empress: Issue 01 – Zia, a silent film actress, goes missing before completing her first talkie film. The studio hires brash P.I. Niles Lance to find her. He soon discovers her disappearance is far from ordinary. Art by Marcelo Salaza, colors by Matheus Bronca, series co-produced by Brian Barr.

IV. Snake: Issue 01 – One of the most fear outlaws in the old west has come home to Cambra to make hell for the town bullies. A gritty, fun western with attitude. Art by Alex Reis, colors by Nimesh Morarji.

V. Bang Bang Lucita: Issue 01 – President Grant arrives in town… outlaws in tow to cause trouble. Luckily for President Grant, Lucita, a sexy swashbuckling knife fighter (who works as a chef by day) is ready to swing into action.

VI. Bonus Material (available for first time in print): Protector Vixi: The first couple pages of Issue 01 version 1. An all ages title about a bullied young boy who finds himself the target of vicious animals. Good thing he has his best friend, Vixi, as his protector. Art by Marcelo Salaza, colors by Nimesh Morarji. Xibalba: Issue 01 – The first 11 pages of Xibalba, which is a sister series to Snake and Bang Bang Lucita. Art: Adrian Crisuadi, colors: Nimesh Morarji. Viperous Vixens: Issue 01 concept cover with lines by Alex Reis and colors by Nimesh Morarji Snake: Issue 00 Prologue. A little teaser released that showed Snake’s arrival into Cambra and a little quick smattering of backstory. First time in print. Art by Alex Reis, colors by Nimesh Morarji.

All titles written and lettered by Chuck Amadori

Since she was a child, Pandora has been raised in a strict boarding school in the countryside. When she's courted by a passionate Greek shipping magnate she's barely just met, she quickly becomes a member of the Kyriakos family. But after a first night that brings her to the pinnacle of joy, she overhears a disconcerting tale: "The Kyriakos heirs must follow family tradition and marry a virgin." He didn't love me at all...he only wanted a virgin for his wife! Then Zack finds out the truth: his young twenty-year-old wife made a mistake in her past that turned into a one-night stand?
name: Billionaire Heirs I
